  <reference>
    <title>Portal Backend API Reference</title>
    <partintro>
    <para>
      The portal backend interfaces (named org.freedesktop.impl.portal.*)
      are not directly available to sandboxed applications. The portal
      frontend is using them to carry out portal requests.
    </para>
    </partintro>
